 討論區"},{"pid":"ccb945d3b4ab413c8c5c80c29d539ee70d884731","tid":1966640,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910b3b5ba62c6f7acc9233da312e3b2fc832523d","tid":1966640,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62bf45e16b0e399c2879f25931da63b4af9f6fa0","tid":1966640,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"有冇相關tweet可以推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/rfacantonese/status/1248289751049941001?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frfacantonese%2Fstatus%2F1248289751049941001%3Fs%3D21&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6x1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=dbff93fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frfacantonese%2Fstatus%2F1248289751049941001%3Fs%3D21&h=987d1a1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/rfacantonese/status/1248289751049941001?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"0e33c12d5c5cafdc7d0ccc5472214ea8e4e069c0","tid":1966640,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:14:11.000Z","msg":"但外長奶緊共wo<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>德國外長批評美國應對疫情太慢<br />\n10.04.2020 19:36<br />\n<br />\n德國外長馬斯批評美國，對新型冠狀病毒疫情的應對太慢。馬斯接受《明鏡周刊》訪問時表示，中國採取非常專制的措施去應對疫情，而在美國，疫情就被淡化了一段長時間，做法是兩個極端，都不是歐洲的榜樣。馬斯表示，希望美國因應疫情危機，重新思考與其他國家的國際關係，指美國進取的貿易政策可能損害國家購買防護設備的能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279998&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279998%26csid%3D261_367&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6x1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=449adc29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279998&amp;csid=261_367</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5485372014c2adc4672c7392aa714f3c170bacd